				<td><img src="/skins/default/images/user_IsOffline.gif" alt="Elauriel is not online. Last active: 10/9/2003 12:37:11 AM" border="0" />&nbsp;<a class="SmallBoldText" href="/User/UserProfile.aspx?UserName=Elauriel">Elauriel</a><br></td>
